# Layer 2-PDF: Noto Sans JP fonts are downloaded by scripts/download-fonts.ts
# and subsetted by scripts/subset-fonts.ts (both run via postinstall) instead
# of committed, to keep the repo small. The directory holds:
#   NotoSansJP-{Regular,Bold}.woff           (full ~1.4 MB, source for subset)
#   NotoSansJP-{Regular,Bold}-subset.woff    (~450 KB, what the PDF loads)
# See docs/layer2-pdf-decisions.md §5 and docs/layer2-pdf-perf-decisions.md.
public/fonts/
